# MANAGED_FILES.manifest — the explicit inventory of paths bin/craft-harness
# materializes into a project (from the pack branch) and replaces atomically
# on upgrade. Nothing outside this list is ever touched, apart from the
# launcher's own state under .craft-harness/, the .craft-harness-version
# pointer, and the hook installed at .git/hooks/pre-commit.
swarmforge/constitution/articles/engineering.prompt
swarmforge/constitution/articles/handoffs.prompt
swarmforge/constitution/articles/workflow.prompt
hooks/pre-commit
